column5: Well, maybe not. One day, crew members working on the reality show "River Monsters" were filming near a remote island off the coast of Australia. They were looking for one particular monster, as they tend to do, but found something bizarre instead. While they were driving their boat around the island, a cameraman suddenly saw something in the distance. Fortunately for us, he kept filming as the situation unfolded.
I thought it was going to be funny
That's crazy, he's very lucky to be rescued.
I dont know what reality is anymore with all that scripted Bull on tv.
I broke down and cried while watching this.
Boy did that guy get lucky.......
Did you notice the rabbits foot on his swim trunks?
